{"tid":1862360,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"感動世人，原來美斯帶傷上陣","createTime":"2020-02-04T14:54:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-04T20:31:44.000Z","uid":173952,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d92ec7bb7b396669187c7b798996fe627d303336","tid":1862360,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T14:54:57.000Z","msg":"2月4日訊 據ESPN報導，梅西近幾場比賽都是帶傷出戰。 球員受到左大腿傷病困擾，但是由於球隊鋒線人員短缺，蘇亞雷斯、登貝萊等人均因傷缺陣，所以一直堅持出戰。<br />\n<br />\n 上一場比賽，巴薩2-1萊萬特，梅西貢獻兩次助攻。 據悉，球員是自己主動請求出戰，雖然是帶傷出戰，但是傷勢並不嚴重，不會導致其長期缺席，但是仍然需要謹慎管理。<br />\n<br />\n 據消息人士稱，自塞蒂恩接手巴薩以後，其訓練方式也給梅西的大腿傷勢造成了一定影響。 對於塞蒂恩的訓練方式，消息人士說道：&ldquo;訓練內容不同，球員也會有不同程度的疲勞，這時候有些球員會出現一些疼痛的情況。&rdquo;"},{"pid":"123d2b0f049aa3f378198cbe145a6ccfc416eeff","tid":1862360,"uid":53855,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T15:05:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">雖然是帶傷出戰，但是傷勢並不嚴重</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e14bed573d2b8e6517eb221a2c504fb18741e6dc","tid":1862360,"uid":3747,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T15:07:06.000Z","msg":"登貝萊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b86aa1d1f3b566e3fcf7ca7e3601a60ba6113c3","tid":1862360,"uid":63152,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T15:08:45.000Z","msg":"你日日copy啲支那文post上黎煩唔撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5edb257db759cad5e185ad1264ac40e1d657e35","tid":1862360,"uid":43861,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6b86aa1d1f3b566e3fcf7ca7e3601a60ba6113c3","tid":1862360,"uid":63152,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T15:08:45.000Z","msg":"你日日copy啲支那文post上黎煩唔撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T15:11:09.000Z","msg":"認同"},{"pid":"bb02f8d558b6a1aa8b7efc3afd56f34a5cc9de36","tid":1862360,"uid":173952,"like":6,"dislike":5,"score":1,"quote":{